\subsection{\href{https://beta.lmfdb.org/knowledge/show/doc.knowl.description}{Description field in knowls}}
\begin{definition}\label{doc.knowl.description}
\uses{doc.knowl.context_free,doc.knowl.naming_conventions,doc.knowl.naming_suggestions}
The description field in a Knowl serves as the most accurate description of the Knowl \hyperref[doc.knowl.context_free]{outside of any context}. It is a human-readable version of the Knowl, compliant with the naming \hyperref[doc.knowl.naming_conventions]{conventions} and \hyperref[doc.knowl.naming_suggestions]{suggestions}.
\end{definition}
